meta {
  name: Ready (dependencies)
  type: http
  seq: 2
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/ready
  body: none
  auth: none
}

docs {
  Readiness probe. 200 when every GATING dependency is reachable
  (Postgres, OpenEMR FHIR, LLM); 503 with the failing deps enumerated.
  Langfuse is advisory — a Langfuse outage never returns 503.
}
